ComicInfo.Summary:
The end to the mystery is here!
It’s been a long road to get here, and there have been a lot of dead bodies along the way, but the detective is very near closing the case. All the disparate threads lead back to the crime itself, to the assassination attempt that claimed the lives of the would-be assassins.
Find out how it all went wrong for the comic book artist who put on a mask and declared himself Rorschach.
